  "body": "When we introduced to use `STATICCALL` for `view` and `pure` we enabled that for 0.5.0 only, in order not to break non-compliant `view`/`constant` functions.\r\n\r\nHowever we never made such a commitment for `pure`, since it was newly introduced, so we could have enabled `staticcall` for that unconditionally.",
